# 📦 Project Summary

## What You Have

A **complete, production-grade authentication system** for Next.js SaaS applications with:

### ✅ Authentication
- Google OAuth 2.0 integration
- GitHub OAuth 2.0 integration
- LinkedIn OAuth 2.0 integration
- Session management (JWT-based)
- CSRF protection
- Secure HTTP-only cookies
- Password-less authentication

### ✅ Features
- Sign In page with all 3 providers
- Sign Up page with all 3 providers
- Protected Dashboard page
- User profile API endpoint
- Account management utilities
- TypeScript type definitions
- Error handling with custom error classes
- Input validation utilities
- Constants and configuration

### ✅ Database
- Prisma ORM
- PostgreSQL (configurable to MySQL, SQLite, MongoDB)
- User model with OAuth accounts
- Session storage
- Verification tokens
- Type-safe queries

### ✅ Security
- Protected routes with middleware
- CORS protection
- Session expiration handling
- Rate limiting ready
- Input sanitization
- Error handling without leaking info
- JWT signing and validation

### ✅ Design
- Beautiful, modern UI
- Tailwind CSS styling
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Dark mode ready
- Accessible components
- Loading states
- Error states

### ✅ Documentation
- Complete setup guide (SETUP.md)
