## Database Schema

### User
- `id` (primary key)
- `name` (string, optional)
- `email` (string, unique)
- `emailVerified` (datetime, optional)
- `image` (string, optional)
- `createdAt` (datetime)
- `updatedAt` (datetime)
- Relations: accounts, sessions

### Account
- `id` (primary key)
- `userId` (foreign key)
- `type` (string) - "oauth"
- `provider` (string) - "google", "github", "linkedin"
- `providerAccountId` (string)
- `refresh_token` (string, optional)
- `access_token` (string, optional)
- `expires_at` (integer, optional)
- `token_type` (string, optional)
- `scope` (string, optional)
- `id_token` (string, optional)
- Unique constraint: [provider, providerAccountId]

### Session
- `id` (primary key)
- `sessionToken` (string, unique)
- `userId` (foreign key)
- `expires` (datetime)

### VerificationToken
- `identifier` (string)
- `token` (string, unique)
- `expires` (datetime)
- Unique constraint: [identifier, token]

## Routes

### Public Routes
- `GET /` - Home page
- `GET /auth/signin` - Sign in page
- `GET /auth/signup` - Sign up page
- `POST /api/auth/signin/[provider]` - OAuth sign in
- `GET /api/auth/callback/[provider]` - OAuth callback
- `POST /api/auth/signout` - Sign out

### Protected Routes
- `GET /dashboard` - User dashboard (requires auth)
- `GET /api/user/profile` - Get user profile (requires auth)

## Environment Variables

```env
# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...

# Authentication
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=...
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Google
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=...
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=...

# GitHub
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=...
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=...

# LinkedIn
LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID=...
LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=...

# Mode
NODE_ENV=development
```

## Getting Started Checklist

### Initial Setup (First Time)
- [ ] Install dependencies: `npm install`
- [ ] Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local`
- [ ] Get OAuth credentials from each provider
- [ ] Add credentials to `.env.local`
- [ ] Generate `NEXTAUTH_SECRET`: `openssl rand -base64 32`
- [ ] Push database schema: `npm run db:push`
- [ ] Start dev server: `npm run dev`
- [ ] Test at http://localhost:3000

### Testing
- [ ] Test sign in with Google
- [ ] Test sign in with GitHub
- [ ] Test sign in with LinkedIn
- [ ] Verify dashboard loads
- [ ] Test sign out
- [ ] Verify session persistence

### Customization
- [ ] Update app name/branding
- [ ] Create legal pages (terms, privacy)
- [ ] Customize dashboard
- [ ] Add your logo/favicon
- [ ] Update styling to match brand

### Deployment
- [ ] Build locally: `npm run build`
- [ ] Fix any build errors
- [ ] Choose hosting platform
- [ ] Update OAuth callback URLs for production
- [ ] Deploy!
- [ ] Test on production domain
- [ ] Monitor logs

